These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, billiard, chess, monopoly
City: nizza, rome, hamburg, hannover
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, lacrosse, water-polo
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, coach, manager, writer
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 2. the security-guard is not to the left of the security-guard##8
 3. the writer is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
 5. the security-guard is not to the right of the security-guard##8
 6. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##5
 8. the person traveling to hannover is between the coach and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
 9. the writer is the person traveling to hamburg##1
10. the writer is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
11. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3
12. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
13. the person traveling to hamburg is not to the left of the writer##8
14. the person playing billiard is the manager##1
15. the person playing billiard is not the person who's sport is ice-hockey##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Game         | mah-jongg     | billiard   | monopoly | chess |
| City   | rome | hannover   | nizza   | hamburg  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey  | lacrosse  | water-polo  | cycling |
| Job     | security-guard    | manager | coach     | writer    |

