.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, australian, argentine, turkish
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, tulip, azalea, poppy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, indie, salsa, trance
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, musical, time-travel, thriller
 1. the fan of salsa is between the person watching scientific movies and the fan of indie##2
 2. the australian is not to the right of the person watching musical movies##8
 3. the australian is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3
 4. the malaysian is not to the right of the person watching thriller movies##8
 5. the person watching scientific movies is not to the left of the fan of indie##8
 6. the person who growspoppy is not to the right of the turkish##8
 7. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5
 8. the person watching time-travel movies is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of house is the person watching musical movies##1
10. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
11. the person watching scientific movies is not to the left of the fan of salsa##8
12. the turkish is on the left of the australian##1
13. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person who growstulip##5
14. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
15. the malaysian is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
17. the malaysian is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
18. the person who growstulip is not to the right of the person watching musical movies##8
19. the turkish is on the right of the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Nationality      | malaysian | argentine | turkish  | australian  |
| Flower          | poppy     | tulip | bellflower | azalea  |
