 3. the person driving the bus is not to the left of the person playing chess##8
 4. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the right of the person playing chess##5
 5. the person driving the scooter is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 6. the person playing go is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##8
 7. the person playing whist is not the person who's birthday is in june##6
 8. the person eating pumpkin is somewhere between the person driving the scooter and the person playing whist##7
 9. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the person eating pumpkin##5
10. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person eating pumpkin##3
11. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person eating radish##1
12. the person eating pumpkin is not the person who's birthday is in january##6
13. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the right of the person playing whist##5
14. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing go##1
15. the person driving the bus is not to the right of the person eating pumpkin##8

.:: Answer ::.
