.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-15::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, aristoff, bluemaster, bongani
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, tea, lemonade, fanta
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, gospel, r&b, soul
